{"word":"Revelation","slug":"revelation","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Revelation</b> God reveals Himself to Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=6'>Exo 3:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=14'>Exo 3:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=3'>Exo 6:3</a><br/> The law is revealed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20'>Exo 20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=1'>Lev 1</a><br/> The pattern of the temple is revealed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=28&verse=19'>1Ch 28:19</a><br/> The sonship of Jesus is revealed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=17'>Mat 3:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=17'>Mat 16:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=5'>Mat 17:5</a><br/><a href='S:Inspiration'>Inspiration</a>; <a href='S:Prophecy'>Prophecy</a>; <a href='S:Prophet'>Prophet</a>; <a href='S:Word of God, Inspiration of'>Word of God, Inspiration of</a>"}]}